Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:22.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many Russians who hate the summer sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:27.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We thoroughly and innocently enjoyed those short summer days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:38.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:40.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:41.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sore loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:45.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Sasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:47.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.72,0:00:49.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:14.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,So how was it? Did that break help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:16.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Madame?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:17.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:20.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you took a little break from the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:27.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not that easy to find... the memories of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:29.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Memories of the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:35.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the Mitaka Documents are sometimes referred to as.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:37.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it sound romantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Memories that you can still change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:46.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Would such memories be a blessing, or perhaps a curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:50.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Such a contractor does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:52.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:57.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, I suppose I should go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:01:59.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:01.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:04.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little token of my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I was able to obtain some information.
