Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You can open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:03.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've skimmed the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing less expected from the SVR.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find BK201's room soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.26,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's more fun to leave him to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ikebukuro, huh? That brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.86,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been there before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:27.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The sun felt like it would pierce through my body on that summer day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What, don't you wanna hear my story?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:37.51,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was there before, when I was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:41.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get us something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't open the door if the knocking isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:10.45,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know that getting rough here isn't a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:14.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to have a chat with you, Black Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:41.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:42.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Cockroaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! No friendly fire, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, July!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:24.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Hei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:31.04,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is this too heavy for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:35.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What?! An animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:40.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:53.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They don't serve alcohol in the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:57.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to persuade them in Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:02.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not interested in a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.27,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You seem like someone who drinks like a fish, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:07.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't drink anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:11.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ordered your meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're not drinking, feel free to order anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:16.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,...anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:31.30,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:37.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Cut me some slack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.43,0:07:40.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm Road Runner from those cartoons I used to watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.39,0:07:47.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.98,0:07:54.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,When you find a capable person, you'd do anything to recruit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:56.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's like that no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:08:01.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We will pay you and treat you better than ever before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.98,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great deal for you no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:07.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, I ask that you join our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:12.34,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This deal includes that girl too, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.32,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:19.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite a blunt answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the response I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:24.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Rationally speaking, there's no reason to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We know that she's a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:33.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be fixated on that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.43,0:08:37.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you expect to find Pavlichenko if you're with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.37,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I killed Pavlichenko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:49.95,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that you've been kept in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:54.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this puzzles me even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:58.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't getting attached to that girl or anything, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:01.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Think whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:07.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:10.54,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've already captured Suou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:16.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave now, we will take her, even if it means stopping the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:19.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We've got another trick up our sleeves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:23.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,This remote control will detonate the explosives on this train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you to believe me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:34.92,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure you're not one to make any rash decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why I didn't kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:45.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know why you didn't kill me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:50.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You had several chances to finish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:54.38,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I would've shot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, I would have...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.28,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If Hei wasn't there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.50,0:10:05.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:09.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm really glad I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.16,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,'Why?', you ask. Because we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:15.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a valid reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There are times when we hate each other exactly because we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I used to hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.20,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You were closer to Nika than you should've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:27.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have a crush on him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:31.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted Nika to look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I remember thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:39.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,However, I cannot remember exactly how I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.85,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,that I liked Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.52,0:10:48.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:52.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,that I killed Nika.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:00.03,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(979,472)}Episode 8    \NThe Sun Sways on a Summer Day
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:08.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've got such great taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:11.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Starting off the day in a cafe, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a banana parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:16.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Is stalking people your hobby, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.96,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Given a choice, I'd rather chase after the young virgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,There's your serious look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:25.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I was just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:29.22,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm different from BK201.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:37.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you've heard about someone who helped an adolescent girl escape, out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:39.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't know if it was out of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're getting jealous now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:45.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,The more I dig, the more interesting it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:50.24,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That doll, Izanami, has an incredible power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you see it my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:00.64,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Fundamentally, I trust contractors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:06.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,They won't do something illogical, like getting innocent people involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:11.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But lately, I've heard of a lot of contractors with irregular behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:18.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard that there's been a good number of contractors who committed suicide in the past few years?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:24.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but it was caused by a single doll's powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:31.41,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Izanami sends contractors to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:33.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it that this doll posses such a power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:37.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What they actually plan to do after securing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Section 3 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.48,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't say who...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:48.39,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I told you something interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:51.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,so I expect something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:53.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Something in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:13:00.69,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's written all over your face that you've found something out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:04.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I really want to obtain that doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If possible, I want a certain contractor to commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.19,0:13:12.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that I trust contractors,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but if you ask me whether I like or hate them, the answer is that I clearly hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I got a call a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:23.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,A contractor named Ilya that the SVR dispatched has just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.93,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If yes, I feel like embracing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:34.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,He was a complete psycho from top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:37.47,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,My dear niece was murdered by him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:40.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It was a clear, midsummer morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:48.12,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I haven't been able to love the summer sun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:56.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you understand how I felt when he killed her, even though it was out of duty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:01.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,We hope you enjoyed your ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:05.13,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,In fifteen minutes, we will be at our last stop, Oomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:08.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:11.72,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you think of revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.46,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.52,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What were you afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.58,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That you would meet the same fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:19.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Or were you looking for profit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.81,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That man was indeed a psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Not because he was a contractor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:29.40,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,but because he was a failure as a human that he became an abominable contractor. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:37.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't do anything outside your logical understanding, despite being a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.14,0:14:42.36,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have the guts to kill the passengers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.89,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Commence the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the train and get Suou out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:14:59.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, making me run through the whole train...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.67,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.57,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Run, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.61,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm chasing after Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.94,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let her escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.83,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You have to capture her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:19.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:24.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July, where is Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:26.09,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,July...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:24.03,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up and come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.55,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:49.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya! You got her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:13.19,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we talk this over?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:16.71,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:19.84,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.07,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:43.44,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill Ilya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.72,0:18:56.87,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.21,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:00.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:25.91,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot, Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.33,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.94,0:19:50.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:54.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Suou, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:19:57.97,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You would have been killed if you hadn't shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:10.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine if that's the only way to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.00,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.25,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:24.08,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:25.63,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Which is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:30.42,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Should I have shot? Was I supposed to shoot this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You told me not to shoot back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:35.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.02,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not blaming you for shooting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:46.59,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Suou?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:51.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! July!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.79,0:20:54.88,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Hei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:56.66,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.82,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.15,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I wish it was summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:10.18,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's better this way... so I can live without hating the summer sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.77,0:21:17.49,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, we can no longer have fun like when we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:23.90,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.43,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:32.78,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:35.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed your referrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:48.79,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot prove my existence, or my involvement with the Syndicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:52.80,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know how big the Syndicate is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:57.65,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met with the contractor who had seen the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:59.29,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,then this would be the only lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:02.68,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing particularly odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:06.23,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I hate doing this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:24.80,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kureteku yuubae ni senaka osarete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:24.80,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}My back is pressed by the darkening glow of dusk
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:35.31,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Arukidasu kage ga shimesu hou e
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.96,0:22:35.31,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I start walking toward where my shadow points
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:44.87,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Taenai ikutsu mo no deai to wakare o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:44.87,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Repeating the many, ceaseless encounters and partings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:51.05,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Kurikaeshi doko e mukau no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:51.05,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where do I head to?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.80,0:22:56.15,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Hito wa dare mo mayoinagara
Dialogue: 1,0:22:50.80,0:22:56.15,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}For all people, while they are lost,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.78,0:23:00.91,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}tsumi to iu na no sadame o seotte
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.78,0:23:00.91,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}they bear the fate known as sin
Dialogue: 3,0:23:00.68,0:23:09.56,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Sore de mo nao ikiru imi o shiru darou
Dialogue: 3,0:23:00.68,0:23:09.56,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Nevertheless, I'll still learn of the meaning to live, right?
Dialogue: 4,0:23:09.38,0:23:14.65,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Bokura wa sou Day by Day
Dialogue: 4,0:23:09.38,0:23:14.65,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}That's right, Day by Day,
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.39,0:23:21.60,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}ashita e tsuzuku michi no tochuu de
Dialogue: 5,0:23:14.39,0:23:21.60,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}we're midway on the road leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 6,0:23:21.23,0:23:29.19,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again kimi to futari no mama
Dialogue: 6,0:23:21.23,0:23:29.19,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Now Say It Again, though it'd be great if
Dialogue: 7,0:23:29.11,0:23:39.48,EDR,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}irareta nara ii no ni naa...
Dialogue: 7,0:23:29.11,0:23:39.48,EDE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I could remain together with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:47.74,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Tokyo might be colder than Russia...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:50.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, you'll catch a cold if you don't change your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:56.50,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Suou? You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:02.17,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone! Doing well-nya?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.06,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Due to popular demand, I've returned, even if it is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.06,0:24:06.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Kayanuma Kiko here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.35,0:24:10.10,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening XXX. When you need assistance, please call us anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:12.75,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the great detective of your heart, Kurasawa Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.75,0:24:15.99,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, next week we'll be in the city of Haneda and both of us will be there!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:18.53,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Once again, we will fulfill your desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.53,0:24:20.77,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to camp in front of your TV next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.77,0:24:23.35,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,Say... aren't we a little out of place in this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.35,0:24:26.62,DTB-Default,,0,0,0,,If you think it's your duty, you've lost, Boss.